caption_text: Figure S4 SEM images of an uncleaned polymer-sorted CNT array. (a) Before and (b) after annealing
snippet_text:
Figure S4 SEM images of an uncleaned polymer-sorted CNT array. (a) Before and (b) after annealing 
in Ar gas at 350 ℃ for 1 hour. A WD of 5 mm is used to emphasize the material difference. The yellow 
arrow indicates the contrast referece, i.e. bright contrast of the bare substrate near the edge of the CNT 
arrays. White spots circled in red indicate the partial removal of the covered polymers.
